-- Poland's KGHM says signed 5-year credit deal worth $2.5 bln
-- By Adrian Krajewski
-- Fri Jul 11, 2014 11:31AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, July 11 (Reuters) - Europe's No.2 copper producer KGHM <KGH.WA> said on Friday it had signed a 5-year credit deal worth $2.5 billion with a group of international and local lenders.

